    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏦 创建并扩展你的银行</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022560/extras/50667789c879ba077ef8e1892f0a1347.poster.avif?t=1764429445\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022560/extras/50667789c879ba077ef8e1892f0a1347.webm?t=1764429445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022560/extras/50667789c879ba077ef8e1892f0a1347.mp4?t=1764429445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>从一个小小的服务台开始，从零建设属于你的银行。<br>解锁新区域、升级服务、自由规划布局，打造你的专属银行。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >👔 亲自为客户服务</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022560/extras/1c4232ce412fe944634a851327a987f0.poster.avif?t=1764429445\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022560/extras/1c4232ce412fe944634a851327a987f0.webm?t=1764429445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022560/extras/1c4232ce412fe944634a851327a987f0.mp4?t=1764429445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>检查身份证、完成交易、批准贷款、管理排队。<br>客户的耐心会不断下降——节奏没掌握好，他们就会离开。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧪 贷款、费用与研究树</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022560/extras/1f365fc0dd5436b25163b8d0409916ed.poster.avif?t=1764429445\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022560/extras/1f365fc0dd5436b25163b8d0409916ed.webm?t=1764429445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022560/extras/1f365fc0dd5436b25163b8d0409916ed.mp4?t=1764429445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在庞大的研究树中推进，解锁全新系统：<br>更多收入、更好的客户关系、ATM、装饰、广告等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着银行扩张，金融决策也变得重要——设置服务费、管理贷款、选择合适的风险。<br>好的决定让银行成长……坏的决定会拖慢发展。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎨 装饰你的银行</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022560/extras/2296676c7be49700ab3f82b8452c3ad6.poster.avif?t=1764429445\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022560/extras/2296676c7be49700ab3f82b8452c3ad6.webm?t=1764429445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022560/extras/2296676c7be49700ab3f82b8452c3ad6.mp4?t=1764429445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>通过添加装饰，让你的银行更温馨、更专业。<br>每一件装饰都能提升声望并提高客户满意度。<br>更高的声望会吸引更富有、更耐心、利润更高的客户。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎮 你的银行，你的规则</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >设计、升级、研究……一切由你掌控。<br>从小小的网点成长为大型金融中心。</p>",
